        "body": "data: \nid: 0/0\nretry: 3000\n\ndata: {\"jsonrpc\":\"2.0\",\"id\":1,\"result\":{\"tools\":[{\"name\":\"add_note\",\"description\":\"Add a note with the given body text. Returns the new note's id.\\nThe note's title is its first line; there is no separate title field.\",\"inputSchema\":{\"$schema\":\"https://json-schema.org/draft/2020-12/schema\",\"properties\":{\"text\":{\"type\":\"string\"}},\"required\":[\"text\"],\"title\":\"__TangramArgs_add_note\",\"type\":\"object\"}},{\"name\":\"update_note\",\"description\":\"Replace the entire body text of an existing note (last-writer-wins;\\nthere is no partial/merge editing) and stamp its last-edited time.\\nThe first line of the text serves as the note's title. Errors if no\\nnote has the given id.\",\"inputSchema\":{\"$schema\":\"https://json-schema.org/draft/2020-12/schema\",\"properties\":{\"id\":{\"type\":\"string\"},\"text\":{\"type\":\"string\"}},\"required\":[\"id\",\"text\"],\"title\":\"__TangramArgs_update_note\",\"type\":\"object\"}},{\"name\":\"list_notes\",\"description\":\"List all notes, most recently edited first (notes never edited sort\\nby creation time).\",\"inputSchema\":{\"$schema\":\"https://json-schema.org/draft/2020-12/schema\",\"title\":\"__TangramArgs_list_notes\",\"type\":\"object\"}},{\"name\":\"delete_note\",\"description\":\"Delete a note by id. Errors if no note has the given id.\",\"inputSchema\":{\"$schema\":\"https://json-schema.org/draft/2020-12/schema\",\"properties\":{\"id\":{\"type\":\"string\"}},\"required\":[\"id\"],\"title\":\"__TangramArgs_delete_note\",\"type\":\"object\"}},{\"name\":\"create_note\",\"description\":\"Create a new empty note and return its id. Use `update_note` to fill\\nin the body afterwards. This is how the editor UI starts a note.\",\"inputSchema\":{\"$schema\":\"https://json-schema.org/draft/2020-12/schema\",\"title\":\"__TangramArgs_create_note\",\"type\":\"object\"}}]}}\nid: 1/0\n\n"
